<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink361">
<l>uyarkaraik kāṉyāṟ ṟavirmaṇa lakaṉṟuṟai</l>
<l>vēṉiṟ pātiri virimalar kuvaiit</l>
<l>toṭalai taiiya maṭavaraṉ makaḷē</l>
<l>kaṇṇiṉuṅ katavaniṉ mulaiyē</l>
<l>mulaiyiṉuṅ katavaniṉ ṟaṭameṉ ṟōḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O simple girl weaving garland, when blossoming flowers  </l>
<l>of summer Pāthiri tree heap in the wide ghat,  </l>
<l>covered with bright sand, near the forest river with high banks! </l>
<l>Your breasts are more angry than your eyes, </l>
<l>and your broad, tender shoulders are more angry than your breasts. </l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
